messages.message:
Hi team, a partner asked, if its possible to exclude inline images, like icons, in an email?
They are having all the icons like linkedin, fb, instagram etc as an image in AiHub and are currently classified as others.

can you clarify your question? i assume you’re asking about Build?
• can you provide an example doc?
• what is the desired classification label for that example doc?
• what are the classes in this Build project?
Inline images are included as a part of the email body. But curious to learn more about the user story like Serena mentioned
